<section id="sec-01">
<title>Atoms and Molecules</title>
<para id="para-10">An atom is the smallest unit of an element.</para>
<para id="para-11">A molecule consists of two or more atoms joined by <m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><m:mrow><m:mi>σ</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> bonds.</para>
</section>

<section id="sec-02">
<title>Chemical Formulas</title>
<para id="para-20">The formula for water is H<sub>2</sub>O.</para>
<note id="note-01" class="link-to-learning">
<para id="para-note">Visit this site to learn more.</para>
</note>
</section>
